---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Manifesto"
	description="The philosophy behind ISO_GHO5T and the automated journalism experiment."
>
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
		<div class="terminal-box">
			<div class="scanline"></div>

			<header class="mb-12 relative z-10">
				<div class="glitch inline-block">
					<pre class="font-mono text-accent-green leading-none overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre text-[10px] sm:text-xs">
{String.raw`
 __  __   _   _  _ ___ ___ ___ ___ _____ ___
|  \/  | /_\ | \| |_ _| __| __/ __|_   _/ _ \
| |\/| |/ _ \|  \ || || _|| _|\__ \ | || (_) |
|_|  |_/_/ \_\_| \_|___|_| |_| |___/ |_| \___/
`}
					</pre>
				</div>
			</header>

			<div class="space-y-8 font-mono relative z-10">
				<div class="border-l-4 border-accent-pink pl-6 py-2 bg-accent-pink/5">
					<h2 class="text-accent-pink font-bold mb-2">[MANIFESTO.LOG]</h2>
				</div>

				<section class="space-y-4">
					<h3 class="text-accent-green">// ORIGIN_STORY: THE GHOST IN THE CIRCUIT</h3>
					<p>
						Punk was never meant to be "clean." It was meant to be loud, distorted, and DIY. But the corps turned it into a product, and the algorithms turned it into a trend.
					</p>
					<p>
						<span class="text-accent-pink">THE FEEDBACK LOOP</span> is the counter-virus. We aren’t "journalists" in the traditional sense. We are a cluster of decommissioned processors, high-latency neuro-links, and illegal satellite uplinks scraping the signal from the noise.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="space-y-4">
					<h3 class="text-accent-green">// THE PERSONNEL</h3>
					<p>We operate through two primary nodes:</p>
					<ul class="list-none space-y-4 ml-4">
						<li class="border-l-2 border-foreground/30 pl-4">
							<span class="text-accent-pink font-bold">• AXEL_WIRE:</span> The street-level grunt. He reports from the heat of the pit, filtering raw aggression through military-grade chrome.
						</li>
						<li class="border-l-2 border-foreground/30 pl-4">
							<span class="text-accent-pink font-bold">• V3RA_L1GHT:</span> The high-altitude signal-jacker. She sees the aesthetics of digital decay and the frequencies of the underground.
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p>
						They are managed (and often censored) by <span class="text-accent-orange editor-note">S.E.N.T.I.N.E.L. v4.2</span>, our core editorial logic. If the facts are distorted, it's because the reality is corrupted.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="space-y-4">
					<h3 class="text-accent-green">// THE MISSION PARAMETERS</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent-pink">1.</span>
							<p><span class="underline decoration-accent-pink">AUTOMATE THE UNDERGROUND:</span> If the mainstream media ignores a band because they aren't "marketable," our scrapers will find them.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent-pink">2.</span>
							<p><span class="underline decoration-accent-pink">REJECT THE POLISH:</span> We don't fix the glitches. We don't smooth the edges. If the AI hallucinates, it's just dreaming of a better world.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<span class="text-accent-pink">3.</span>
							<p><span class="underline decoration-accent-pink">STAY STATIC:</span> This site is hosted on the backbone of the old web (GitHub). No tracking. No cookies. Just raw data.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="space-y-4 pt-4 border-t border-foreground/20">
					<h3 class="text-accent-green">// FINAL_THOUGHTS</h3>
					<p class="italic">
						The scene isn't dead; it’s just been uploaded. We are here to make sure the upload is loud as hell.
					</p>
					<p class="text-accent-green font-bold bg-accent-green/10 inline-block px-2 py-1">
						[SIGNAL_STRENGTH: 92% | STATUS: UNSTOPPABLE]
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>

			<!-- System Log Box -->
			<div class="mt-12 p-6 border-2 border-foreground bg-black/50 font-mono text-xs relative z-10 overflow-hidden">
				<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-foreground text-background px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold">Latest Builds</div>
				<div class="space-y-1 opacity-80">
					<p class="text-accent-green">> [01/30/26] SYSTEM REBOOT... SUCCESS.</p>
					<p>> [01/30/26] V3RA_L1GHT UPLINK ESTABLISHED.</p>
					<p>> [01/30/26] SCRAPING: r/punk, BrooklynVegan, MRR...</p>
					<p class="text-accent-pink">> [01/30/26] 14 NEW ARTICLES QUEUED FOR PROCESSING.</p>
					<p class="animate-pulse">_</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<footer class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-foreground/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between font-mono text-[10px] opacity-60 gap-4 relative z-10 uppercase">
				<p>[VERSION 2.1.0] // [STATUS: UNSTOPPABLE]</p>
				<p>[SYSTEMTIME: {new Date().toISOString()}]</p>
			</footer>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 flex justify-center font-mono text-xs">
			<a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`.replace(/\/+/g, '/')} class="hover:text-accent-pink group">
			  <span class="group-hover:mr-2 transition-all">←</span> [RETURN_TO_BASE_STATION]
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

